    max(v.systemicdiastolic) as max_systemicdiastolic
from
    patient p
join 
    vitalperiodic v on p.patientunitstayid = v.patientunitstayid
where
    p.uniquepid = '002-58884'
    and v.observationtime <= '2105-11-12 23:59:59'
group by 
    strftime('%Y', v.observationtime)
order by 
    year;

    WHERE d.diagnosisname LIKE '%chronic kidney disease%'
),
ckd_with_5y AS (
    SELECT
        c.patientunitstayid,
        c.hospitaldischargetime,
        c.hospitaldischargestatus,
        MIN(p2.hospitaldischargetime) AS next_outcome_time,
        p2.hospitaldischargestatus AS status_in_5y
    FROM ckd_patients c
    LEFT JOIN patient p2
        ON c.patientunitstayid = p2.patientunitstayid
        AND p2.hospitaldischargetime > c.hospitaldischargetime
        AND p2.hospitaldischargetime <= datetime(c.hospitaldischargetime, '+5 years')
    GROUP BY c.patientunitstayid
),
outcome_status AS (
    SELECT
        c.patientunitstayid,
        CASE
            WHEN c.status_in_5y IS NULL AND (c.hospitaldischargetime IS NOT NULL)

                THEN NULL
            ELSE NULL

        d.patientunitstayid,
        p.hospitaladmittime,
        p.hospitaldischargetime,
        p.hospitaldischargestatus
    from
        diagnosis d
        join patient p on d.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
    where
        d.diagnosisname = 'wound infection - surgical wound'
),
survival_status as (
    select
        *,
        (julianday(hospitaldischargetime) - julianday(hospitaladmittime)) as days_in_hospital,
        case
            when hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive'
                 or (
                        hospitaldischargestatus = 'expired'
                        and (julianday(hospitaldischargetime) - julianday(hospitaladmittime)) > 730
                    )
            then 1
            else 0
        end as survived_2yr
    from wound_patients
)
select
    count(*) as total_patients,
    sum(survived_2yr) as num_survived_2yr,
    round(1.0 * sum(survived_2yr) / count(*), 4) as two_year_survival_probability
from survival_status;
